cleaned_text: Energy Alchemy by Crystal Streets Crystal Streets is multidimensional - an Energetic Alchemist, Healer, Channel, Ceremonialist, Cosmic Guide, Breathwork Facilitator and Spiritual Coach. Her birth name "Crystal" is reflective of her healing gifts & purpose. She has a special awareness & knowledge of energetics in which she leverages to support others during energy healing sessions and readings. A true Alchemist, she can transmute the darkest, ugliest energy and make it beautiful and light.
